    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深入探索地下基地的深处，逐层推进，最终抵达地面并求得生存。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/18eee3c713799bb2fd7202736d87671f.poster.avif?t=1767691402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/18eee3c713799bb2fd7202736d87671f.webm?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/18eee3c713799bb2fd7202736d87671f.mp4?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏进程</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析居住在每一层的各种 AI 怪物的独特特征。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 AI 机器人 Lumi 的引导下，收集关键的生存物品，并寻找逃离地下设施的路线。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a388d9cf8ff565bd30e892a3e226745b.poster.avif?t=1767691402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a388d9cf8ff565bd30e892a3e226745b.webm?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a388d9cf8ff565bd30e892a3e226745b.mp4?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是被困在地下基地深处的最后一名幸存者。听从 AI Lumi 的指令，躲避潜伏在黑暗中的生物，向地面发起逃亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/8dd5d62f5a8d15791b086ebff03e2ab0.poster.avif?t=1767691402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/8dd5d62f5a8d15791b086ebff03e2ab0.webm?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/8dd5d62f5a8d15791b086ebff03e2ab0.mp4?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心系统 (主要特色)</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的生存方法：每一层的怪物都需要不同的应对策略——包括对环境声音敏感的生物、被直视时会僵直的实体，以及完全不可预测的威胁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/9ef1a8588163ec7edf42e2d7f96482d0.poster.avif?t=1767691402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/9ef1a8588163ec7edf42e2d7f96482d0.webm?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/9ef1a8588163ec7edf42e2d7f96482d0.mp4?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧张的巅峰时刻：在最终逃生前，将开启一段扣人心弦的追逐关卡，整个基地仿佛都在崩塌。体验极致的惊悚感！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a631c7c98ef86b01695e27d70c27dbaf.poster.avif?t=1767691402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a631c7c98ef86b01695e27d70c27dbaf.webm?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176770/extras/a631c7c98ef86b01695e27d70c27dbaf.mp4?t=1767691402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内容警告</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >警告：本游戏包含以下元素：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强烈且持续的恐怖元素，以及突发性的惊吓演出 (Jumpscares)。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暴力与血腥 (Gore)。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者寄语</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏完全由一名 19 岁的学生独立策划、开发和制作。</p>",
